title: Fortune Feimster
itunes:title: Fortune Feimster
description:
Comedian Fortune Feimster (Office Christmas Party, The Happy Time Murders, The Mindy Project) and Whitney talk about rats and cats that run wild around Disney World, Jennifer Aniston, sex toy lube, and play a new game Benton invented called "Think or Drink." Be sure to watch Fortune's Netflix special Sweet and Salty and see her on her 2 Sweet 2 Salty Tour tickets on sale now.  Fortune's podcast is Sincerely Fortune.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
